Adding Logo 11

Steps

Adding Colaberry Logo

Ø  Click on Insert from ribbon.

Ø  Then click on Image in Elements

Ø  Select the Image from the Extracted file

Ø  General:  X - Position = 0, Y - Position = 0, Width = 197 and Height = 55

Scaling: Normal

Steps

Adding Project Logo

Ø  Click on Insert from ribbon.

Ø  Then click on Image in Elements

Ø  Select the Image from the Extracted file

Ø  General:  X - Position = 1168, Y - Position = 0, Width = 112 and Height = 55

                Ø Scaling: Normal
